            "actor": "narrator",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "Beleth's broom closet"
        },
        {
            "actor": "narrator",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "<i>*knock knock*</i>"
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:beleth",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "Come in."
        },
        {
            "actor": "backdrop",
            "action": "show",
            "view": "bg1b"
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:median",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "Hey, we’re done. Pack it up."
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:beleth",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "What? That’s it? That’s all there is to it?"
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:median",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "Yep."
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:beleth",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "It seems a bit... I dunno."
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:median",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "Anticlimactic?"
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:beleth",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "Yeah."
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:median",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "That’s a good thing. The best possible outcome, actually."
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:median",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "There are still things for you to do anyway, I’m sure."
        },
        {
            "actor": "backdrop",
            "action": "show",
            "view": "bg1c"
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:beleth",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "Like what?"
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:median",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "You’ll have to talk to Andre, later. I’m leaving him with a pamphlet on what Trebol’s going to need as it recovers."
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:median",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "It was originally going to be a document, but a little bird told me that Andre loves to read pamphlets, so... I turned it into a pamphlet."
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:beleth",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "Hmm."
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:median",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "But as for me, personally, I’m done."
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:beleth",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "What if the disease comes back? Can that happen?"
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:median",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "Oh, it can happen. It probably will, actually; there are bound to be a few stragglers who managed to escape getting the medicine."
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:median",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "But it won’t be a big deal. I’m going to Vaxine over in Cardios to share the formula for the medicine, so they’ll be able to supply all of the Blackjack Isles with a cure for any new cases."
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:median",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "The big deal now is mental recovery. Trebol lost a good deal of citizens, and morale here is pretty low."
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:median",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "Things will pick up, though. They always do. It’s all part of the healing process."
        },
        {
            "actor": "backdrop",
            "action": "show",
            "view": "bg1d"
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:median",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "Before I leave, I am prescribing you one week of vacation."
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:beleth",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "What? Really?"
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:median",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "I’ve already cleared it with Andre."
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:median",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "Try not to have too much fun."
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:median",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "Take care of yourself!"
        },
        {
            "actor": "jukebox",
            "action": "stop"
        },
        {
            "actor": "curtain",
            "action": "lower"
        },
        {
            "actor": "jukebox",
            "action": "play",
            "track": "belethbored"
        },
