        },
        {
            "actor": "char:biff",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "Hey, Beleth! I’m done!"
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:biff",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "And I get a week’s worth of vacation! How awesome is that?"
        },
        {
            "actor": "backdrop",
            "action": "show",
            "view": "bg1j"
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:beleth",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "Pretty awesome, yeah. I was surprised when Median prescribed it to me."
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:biff",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "Yeah, she said something about mental fatigue and accumulated stress, but whatever. I’ll take a week’s vacation any day of the week."
        },
        {
            "actor": "backdrop",
            "action": "show",
            "view": "bg1k1"
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:biff",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "Ahh... Peace at last."
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:biff",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "..."
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:beleth",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "..."
        },
        {
            "actor": "backdrop",
            "action": "show",
            "view": "bg1k2"
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:biff",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "What are you gonna do with your vacation?"
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:beleth",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "I don’t know. It’s been so long since my last break, I’ve kinda forgotten how to actually, uh, take one."
        },
        {
