        },
        {
            "actor": "char:biff",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "Well."
        },
        {
            "actor": "jukebox",
            "action": "play",
            "track": "belethwhatever"
        },
        {
            "actor": "backdrop",
            "action": "show",
            "view": "bg2a1"
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:biff",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "Hey! There’s always movies! And cartoons!"
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:biff",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "There’s this cool new horror movie coming out next week, you wanna go see it?"
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:beleth",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "What is it?"
        },
        {
            "actor": "backdrop",
            "action": "show",
            "view": "bg2a2"
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:biff",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "It’s “Zombie 2: Zombier”. It’s the sequel to “Pick Your Brain”."
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:beleth",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "Ugh."
        },
        {
            "actor": "backdrop",
            "action": "show",
            "view": "bg2b1"
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:biff",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "What’s the ugh for? It’s a good movie franchise!"
        },
        {
            "actor": "backdrop",
            "action": "show",
            "view": "bg2b2"
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:beleth",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "Those things are so inaccurate."
        },
        {
            "actor": "backdrop",
            "action": "show",
            "view": "bg2b1"
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:biff",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "I never said it was accurate! A movie doesn’t have to be accurate to be good. It’s entertaining."
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:biff",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "It’s the same thing with that comic you’re reading."
        },
        {
            "actor": "backdrop",
            "action": "show",
            "view": "bg2b2"
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:beleth",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "My graphic novel, you mean."
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:biff",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "Yeah, that. Whatever. “Suit Yourself” isn’t that accurate either, buddy."
        },
        {
            "actor": "backdrop",
            "action": "show",
            "view": "bg2c1"
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:beleth",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "It portrays things way more correctly than zombie movies do! "
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:beleth",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "The range of emotions the characters display make them almost more real than the real thing!"
        },
        {
            "actor": "backdrop",
            "action": "show",
            "view": "bg2c2"
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:biff",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "Then you’ll love Zombie 2! It’s a story about forbidden love, society’s expectations, and having the courage to break out of those expectations!"
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:biff",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "The main character, Zombiette, falls for a modern-day version of Prince Charming."
        },
        {
            "actor": "backdrop",
            "action": "show",
            "view": "bg2d1"
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:beleth",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "Barf. That’s more than overdone."
        },
        {
            "actor": "backdrop",
            "action": "show",
            "view": "bg2d2"
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:biff",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "Come on. Give it a try."
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:beleth",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "..."
        },
        {
            "actor": "backdrop",
            "action": "show",
            "view": "bg2d3"
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:beleth",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "Fine. On one condition."
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:biff",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "What is it?"
        },
        {
            "actor": "backdrop",
            "action": "show",
            "view": "bg2e1"
        },
        {
            "actor": "char:beleth",
            "action": "say",
            "text": "You have to watch a movie I choose afterward. And you have to sit through the whole thing."
        },
        {
